ox to Mount McGregor |publisher=D. Appleton |location=New York |year=1887 |oclc=558211659 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Brands |first=H. W. |authorlink=H.W. Brands|title=The Man Who Saved the Union: Ulysses S. Grant in War and Peace |publisher=Doubleday |location=New York |year=2012 |isbn=978-0-385-53241-9 |url=https://archive.org/details/manwhosavedunion0000bran |url-access=registration |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Calhoun |first=Charles W. |title=The Presidency of Ulysses S. Grant |authorlink=Charles W. Calhoun |publisher=University Press of Kansas |location=Lawrence |year=2017 |isbn=978-0-7006-2484-3 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=KWXdswEACAAJ |ref=harv}} scholarly review and response by Calhoun at {{DOI|10.14296/RiH/2014/2270}}\n* {{cite book |last=Campbell |first=Edwina S. |title=Citizen of a Wider Commonwealth: Ulysses S. Grant's Postpresidential Diplomacy |publisher=Southern Illinois University Press |location= Illinois |year=2016 |isbn=978-0-8093-3478-0 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=aZS-CwAAQBAJ |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Chernow |first=Ron |authorlink=Ron Chernow |title=Grant |publisher=Penguin Press |location=New York |year=2017 |isbn=978-1-59420-487-6 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wRYcDgAAQBAJ |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Coolidge |first=Louis |year=1917 |title=Ulysses S. Grant |publisher=Houghton Mifflin Co. |location=Boston & New York |url=https://archive.org/details/ulyssessgrant00morsgoog|ref=harv}}; scholarly review at {{DOI|10.14296/RiH/2014/2270}}\n* {{cite journal| last=Dorsett |first=Lyle W. |title=The Problem of Ulysses S. Grant's Drinking During the Civil War |journal=Hayes Historical Journal |volume=4 |issue=2 |year=1983 |pages=37\u201349 |url=http://www.rbhayes.org/research/hayes-historical-journal-the-problem-of-ulysses-s.-grant/ |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web|title=Election of 1872|url=http://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/showelection.php?year=1872|publisher=American Presidency Project \u2122|ref={{sfnRef|Election